“Sanson Ki Mala” is a beautiful and spiritually uplifting song by the legendary qawwali singer
Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan. The song is based on a traditional bhajan (devotional song) that was originally written by the famous saint and poet Meerabai, expressing deep love and devotion to Lord Krishna. Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan’s rendition blends his powerful voice with classical qawwali elements, creating a soulful and meditative experience.
